# Deploy ONLY web/ to Vercel — never the Rust runtime / build code, so the
# Vercel deployment stays tiny. The Vercel project's Root Directory is set to
# `web`, which scopes the deploy; this list is belt-and-suspenders for the
# source upload.
/src
/target
/tests
/crates
/examples
/docs
/benches
/assets
/templates
/.github
/Cargo.toml
/Cargo.lock
*.rs
